cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SI 

The paper proposes a new activation function for neural networks, which is relevant to the subfield of neural networks and deep learning (cs.NE). The activation function is computationally efficient and memory-efficient, which is relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also tests the activation function on toy problems for feedforward and recurrent networks, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and signal processing (cs.SI).
